---
import Page from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
---
<Page
  title="Tip Jar"
  description="The Prompt Kitchen is free and always will be. If it's been useful, a tip keeps the kitchen running."
>
  <section class="support-hero container">
    <h1>♥ Tip Jar</h1>
    <p class="support-sub">The Prompt Kitchen is free, open, and always will be. If it's saved you time or made AI more useful, a small tip keeps the lights on and new recipes coming.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="container support-layout">

    <div class="support-main">
      <div class="support-card">
        <div class="support-emoji">☕</div>
        <h2>Buy me a coffee</h2>
        <p>The simplest way to say thanks. One-time, no account needed.</p>
        <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
          Buy me a coffee →
        </a>
        <p class="support-note">Opens Buy Me a Coffee — a trusted tip platform used by thousands of creators.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="support-card support-card--alt">
        <div class="support-emoji">🍕</div>
        <h2>Buy me a slice</h2>
        <p>A bigger tip for a bigger appetite. Goes directly toward hosting, research, and new content.</p>
        <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large">
          Buy me a slice →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="support-sidebar">
      <div class="sidebar-card">
        <h3>🍳 What your tip funds</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Hosting &amp; infrastructure</li>
          <li>New recipes and guides</li>
          <li>AI tool research &amp; testing</li>
          <li>Keeping the site ad-free</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebar-card">
        <h3>💬 Other ways to help</h3>
        <ul class="other-ways">
          <li><a href="/submit/">Submit a recipe</a> — share a prompt that works for you</li>
          <li>Tell a friend who uses AI</li>
          <li>Star the project on GitHub</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebar-card sidebar-card--warm">
        <p>"Free and open" isn't a business model — it's a commitment. Thanks for being part of it. 🙏</p>
      </div>
    </aside>

  </div>
</Page>

<style>
.support-hero {
  padding: var(--s12) 0 var(--s8);
  max-width: var(--container-narrow);
}
.support-hero h1 {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  margin: 0 0 var(--s4);
}
.support-sub {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: var(--text-2);
  line-height: 1.65;
  max-width: 560px;
  margin: 0;
}

.support-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 260px;
  gap: var(--s8);
  padding-bottom: var(--s20);
  align-items: start;
}

.support-main {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--s5);
}

.support-card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--r4);
  padding: var(--s8);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--s4);
}
.support-card--alt {
  background: var(--bg-alt);
}
.support-emoji {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  line-height: 1;
}
.support-card h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  margin: 0;
}
.support-card p {
  color: var(--text-2);
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
}
.support-note {
  font-size: 0.78rem !important;
  color: var(--text-3) !important;
}

.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--s2);
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  border-radius: var(--r2);
  transition: all var(--t-fast);
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  cursor: pointer;
  align-self: flex-start;
}
.btn-large { padding: var(--s3) var(--s6); font-size: 1rem; }
.btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border-color: var(--accent); }
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent-hover); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }
.btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--text); border-color: var(--border); }
.btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--bg-alt); color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }

/* Sidebar */
.support-sidebar {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--s4);
  position: sticky;
  top: calc(var(--nav-h) + var(--s4));
}
.sidebar-card {
  background: var(--surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--r3);
  padding: var(--s5);
}
.sidebar-card--warm {
  background: var(--accent-light);
  border-color: var(--accent-border);
}
.sidebar-card--warm p {
  color: var(--text-2);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
  font-style: italic;
}
.sidebar-card h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 1rem;
  margin: 0 0 var(--s3);
}
.sidebar-card ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--s2);
}
.sidebar-card li {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: var(--text-2);
}
.other-ways a {
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 600;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .support-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .support-sidebar { position: static; }
}
</style>
